erald.com/view.php?ud=20200221000249 |title=Airlines to suspend more flights over coronavirus |date=21 February 2020 |work=The Korea Herald |access-date=21 February 2020 |agency=Yonhap}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"iLVLj\">{{cite news |last1=Song |first1=Seung-hyun |url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200221000554 |title=Foreign artists delay concerts in Korea due to spread of COVID-19 |date=21 February 2020 |work=[[The Korea Herald]] |access-date=21 February 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"mNKf7\">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-51836898 |title=Coronavirus in South Korea: How 'trace, test and treat' may be saving lives |first=Laura |last=Bicker |work=BBC |date=12 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"CvyZS\">{{cite web |title=South Korea's Drive-Through Testing For Coronavirus Is Fast\u2014And Free |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/03/13/815441078/south-koreas-drive-through-testing-for-coronavirus-is-fast-and-free |publisher=NPR |accessdate=16 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Wypis\">{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/03/south-korea-coronavirus-lessons-quick-easy-tests-monitoring-200319011438619.html |title=South Korea's coronavirus lessons: Quick, easy tests; monitoring |first=Kelly |last=Kasulis |date=19 March 2020 |publisher=Al Jazeera}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"fdhQW\">{{cite web |title=South Korea reports lowest number of new cases |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-52001837 |website=BBC News |accessdate=23 March 2020 |date=23 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"20200313nytime\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/13/world/asia/coronavirus-china-conspiracy-theory.html |title=China spins tale that the US Army started the coronavirus epidemic |date=13 March 2020 |work=[[The New York Times]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"zU2Bk\">{{cite web |title=Coronavirus disease 2019 |url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019 |publisher=[[World Health Organization]] |accessdate=15 March 2020}}</ref>\n<ref