iest-site-over-virus%2f2020%2f02%2f26%2fc86ec712-5918-11ea-8efd-0f904bdd8057_story.html |title=Iran news agencies report Friday prayers canceled in Tehran |first=Jon |last=Gambrell |agency=Associated Press |work=[[The Washington Post]]}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HFdq4\">{{cite news |url=https://www.ft.com/content/b57610e4-5926-11ea-abe5-8e03987b7b20 |title=Saudi Arabia bans Mecca pilgrimages over coronavirus fears |first1=Ahmed |last1=Al Omran |first2=Simeon |last2=Kerr |date=27 February 2020 |work=Financial Times}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"V8C1i\">{{cite news |url=https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/coronavirus-saudi-arabia-bans-umrah-pilgrimage-residents-and-citizens |title=Coronavirus: Saudi Arabia bans all Umrah pilgrimage to Mecca |date=4 March 2020 |work=Middle East Eyes}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"8med7\">{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2641054.html |title=All of next week's UEFA matches postponed |date=13 March 2020 |publisher=UEFA}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"sSb4h\">{{cite web |url=https://www.squawka.com/en/premier-league-suspended-coronavirus-liverpool-title/ |title=Premier League 2019/20 season suspended after coronavirus cases at Chelsea, Arsenal and more |author=Edwards, Harry |date=13 March 2020 |work=squawka.com}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"HY7m9\">{{cite news |last1=Close |first1=David |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/us/nba-season-suspended-spt-trnd/index.html |title=NBA suspends its season after player tests positive for coronavirus|access-date=12 March 2020|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312100641/https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/us/nba-season-suspended-spt-trnd/index.html|archive-date=12 March 2020 |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]] |last2=Jackson |first2=Amanda}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"rixzT\">{{cite web |url=https://www.nhl.com/news/nhl-coronavirus-status/c-316155530 |title=NHL statement on coronavirus |date=12 March 2020 |publisher=National Hockey League|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314025848/https: